; Copy to .npmrc (gitignored) and set NPM_TOKEN in your shell env, OR
; replace ${NPM_TOKEN} with the literal token for machine-wide auth.
;
; Get a token: npmjs.com → Access Tokens → Generate New Token
;   - Granular (preferred): scope to "@crabbykit", "Packages and scopes" write
;   - Classic "Automation": works too, bypasses 2FA for publish
;
; Verify: npm whoami

//registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
